  <brief_title>Effect of Ferric Carboxymaltose on Exercise Capacity in Patients With Iron Deficiency and Chronic Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <acronym>EFFECT-HF</acronym>
  <official_title>Multicentre, Prospective, Randomised, 2-arm Study to Assess the Impact of Ferric Carboxymaltose on Exercise Capacity in Chronic Heart Failure Patients With Iron Deficiency</official_title>
  <sponsors>
