  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to confirm that treatment with IV ferric carboxymaltose improves
      exercise capacity, physical functioning and quality of life in patients with iron deficiency
      and chronic heart failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
